      "note": "",
      "abstract": "Relates to enacting the \"NYCHA HVAC repair act\"; provides for the heating and cooling of properties including dwelling units owned by the New York city housing authority through the installation of geothermal or air source heat pumps and for the replacement of lighting on New York city housing authority property with LED bulbs."
